<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
  <title>404 - Page Not Found | MBK Tech</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist. Return to MBK Tech's home page or contact support for assistance." />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow" />
  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--darker, #0a1414), var(--primary-dark, #1769aa));
      color: var(--text, #e0f7fa);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
    }
    .hero-404 {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 70vh;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 1rem 2rem 1rem;
    }
    .hero-404 h1 {
      font-size: 5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--accent, #00b894);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
      text-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(33,150,243,0.15);
    }
    .hero-404 p {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--text-light, #b2dfdb);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    .cta-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(.4, 0, .2, 1);
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .btn-primary {
      background-color: var(--accent, #00b894);
      color: var(--dark, #101c1c);
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background-color: var(--secondary, #43e97b);
    }
    .btn-outline {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: var(--accent, #00b894);
      border: 2px solid var(--accent, #00b894);
    }
    .btn-outline:hover {
      background-color: rgba(0, 184, 148, 0.1);
      color: var(--dark, #101c1c);
    }
    .notfound-img {
      width: 180px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 4px 24px rgba(33,150,243,0.15));
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .hero-404 h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
      .notfound-img { width: 120px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <section class="hero-404">
    <h1>404</h1>
    <p>Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.<br>
      It might have been moved, deleted, or never existed.<br>
      Let's get you back on track!</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary">Go to Homepage</a>
      <a href="/Support&Contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contact Support</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>